2. Add or update .gitattributes

Create (or edit) .gitattributes:

*.sh text eol=lf
*.py text eol=lf
Dockerfile text eol=lf
*.yml text eol=lf
*.yaml text eol=lf

This forces Git to keep Linux line endings for those files.

3. Renormalize the repository
git add --renormalize .
